<div id="review_20417091" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/20417091" />
    <a title="Josephine Morris" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/737844-josephine-morris"><img alt="Josephine Morris" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1202329770p2/737844.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/20417091?book_show_action=true">Apr 17, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Josephine Morris" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Josephine Morris" href="/user/show/737844-josephine-morris">Josephine Morris</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780743291583" href="/book/show/2485978.Farm_Sanctuary">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer20417091" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2556808373728850451">This book so eloquently describes the plight of the over 10 billion (yes you read that right, 10 billion) farm animals that endure suffering every year in the United States for human consumption. Baer has reminded me the importance of living not only a vegetarian lifestyle but truly a compassionate vegan lifestyle. I am continually surprised at how positive he is about the small steps of progress being made in such a horrifying industry.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


