        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2135120348" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12528724513028842500"><strong>Excellent Read on Farm Animals</strong><br/><br/>Learned a lot. Not at all what I expected. Great companion book to Eating Animals. Gene Bauer does not come off preachy or judgmental but seems to be caring -- about PEOPLE, too. Not just the animals. Now, if only I could convince my family to allow me to adopt a rescued farm factory pig...!!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


