<li class='cover' id='bookCover_6604712'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6604712-eating-animals"><img alt="Eating Animals" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1327877480l/6604712._SX98_.jpg" />
